high_descs: Turn left and walk forward to face the sink.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Turn left and step forward to face the counter to the right of the stove.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Place the knife on the counter.
Pick up a slice of potato on the counter.
Take a step to the right to face the stove.
Place the potato slice in the pot.
Pick up the pot with a potato slice in it.
Turn right and walk forward to face the sink.
Place the pot in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To put a potato slice in a pot and place it in the sink.

high_descs: turn left and walk straight to face the kitchen sink
pick up the knife in the sink
turn around, walk straight to the opposite wall, then face right to see the end of the counter top
slice the potato in front of the salt shaker
place the knife on the counter top in front of the pan
pick up a slice of potato on the counter
face the stove top to the right of the counter
place the potato slice in the pot on the left side of the stove top
pick up the pot on the stove top
bring the pot to the sink
place the pot in the sink on the left hand side
anns.task_desc: slice the potato and place it in the stove top pot, bring the filled pot to the sink

high_descs: Turn left and go to the sink
Grab the knife out of the sink
Turn around and go to the counter to the left of the oven
Slice the potato on the counter
Put the knife on the counter
Grab a slice of potato off the counter
Turn right and go to the oven
Put the potato slice in the pot on the stove
Grab the pot off of the stove
Turn right and go to the sink
Put the pot in the sink
anns.task_desc: Putting a pot with a potato slice in it in the sink
